title: 8: Stiff Socks Goes to a Wax Museum
itunes:title: Stiff Socks Goes to a Wax Museum
description:
Stiff Socks go to Madame Tussaud's Wax Museum. They learn that Jason Derulo is somehow famous enough to have a wax statue and that even wax J-Lo has cake.
